'''Gybellom Osa''' was a [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustan]] trader with a coarse personality but a heart of gold.

==Biography==
During his travels he met up with [[Hyobu Sulloran]], a [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] who was educating himself on how to be a space merchant. The two of them traveled far, making many profits and encountering things not usually seen by either Sullustan or [[Human/Legends|Human]] eyes. However, while they on a routine cargo run, an [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Imperial Star Destroyer]] stopped them for an ordinary cargo inspection. Though the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] were very thorough in their searches, they found nothing incriminating. They were about to let the two leave when the officer performing the search received a message on his [[Comlink/Legends|comlink]]. Without any explanation, the Imperials imprisoned Sulloran and left Osa on his ship. This was not so fortunate for Osa as one would believe, however, as the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] soon ended his life by destroying the entire ship in a volley of [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] fire.

